       xml:space="preserve"
       style="font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:0%;font-family:sans-serif;letter-spacing:0px;word-spacing:0px;display:inline;fill:#000000;fill-opacity:1;stroke:none;stroke-width:1px;stroke-linecap:butt;stroke-linejoin:miter;stroke-opacity:1"
       x="-562.23138"
       y="1071.4866"
       id="text3595"><tspan
         sodipodi:role="line"
         x="-562.23138"
         y="1071.4866"
         id="tspan3599"
         style="font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:bold;font-stretch:normal;font-family:sans-serif;-inkscape-font-specification:'sans-serif Bold'">Fonts for Latin, Cyrillic, Greek and etc.:</tspan><tspan
         sodipodi:role="line"
         x="-562.23138"
         y="1091.7991"
         id="tspan3603"><tspan
   style="font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-family:Universalia;-inkscape-font-specification:Universalia"
   id="tspan3657">Universalia</tspan> (no <tspan
   style="font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';-inkscape-font-specification:'Times New Roman, '"
   id="tspan3659">Times New Roman</tspan>, because <tspan
   style="font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-family:Universalia;-inkscape-font-specification:Universalia"
   id="tspan3661">Universalia</tspan> is more</tspan><tspan
         sodipodi:role="line"
         x="-562.23138"
         y="1113.613"
         id="tspan3639">accurated, better and updated font then <tspan
   style="font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';-inkscape-font-specification:'Times New Roman, '"
   id="tspan3663">TNR</tspan>, it also have</tspan><tspan
         sodipodi:role="line"
         x="-562.23138"
         y="1133.9564"
         id="tspan3651">support of Unicode 8.0) or <tspan
   style="font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-family:UniversaliaPlus;-inkscape-font-specification:UniversaliaPlus"
   id="tspan3665">Universalia Plus</tspan> (if first doesnt' supported).</tspan><tspan
         sodipodi:role="line"
         x="-562.23138"
         y="1154.3463"
         id="tspan3667">If both Universalia fonts doesnt' supported, use another accurated</tspan><tspan
         sodipodi:role="line"
         x="-562.23138"
         y="1174.6588"
         id="tspan3671">multisupported <tspan
   style="font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-family:serif;-inkscape-font-specification:serif"
   id="tspan3669">serif</tspan> font.</tspan><tspan
         sodipodi:role="line"
         x="-562.23138"
         y="1195.0487"
         id="tspan3674"> </tspan><tspan
         sodipodi:role="line"
         x="-562.23138"
         y="1215.3612"
         id="tspan3676">Do not use an itallic or bold variants of the font (some letters have own</tspan><tspan
         sodipodi:role="line"
         x="-562.23138"
         y="1235.6737"
         id="tspan3678">itallic or bold form).</tspan></text>
    <text
